resources.string: TRAVWITOR (Traveling With Motor) is a motorbike rental application where you can rent various kinds of motorbikes, from automatic, moped, to clutch in various cities in Indonesia for your various activities in just one application. Motorbike rental conditions are in About the Application (top right corner).

The TRAVWITOR application was created by Ganendra Kalla Radhya. This application was created for the purposes of Assessment 1 Mobpro. Contact WA: 082136428374 Copyright Â© 2024 All Rights Reserved. Documents that must be shown for motorbike rental purposes: 1. SIM C 2. Personal STNK 3. KTP
You can\'t leave it empty, bro / sis!
Please enter the name of the renter
Please enter the length of rental
The following are the choices for Honda Matic motorbikes: 1. Honda Vario 2. Honda Beat 3. Honda Scoopy
The following are the choices for the Honda Moped motorbike: 1. Honda Supra X 2. Honda Revo 3. Honda Supra GTR
The following are the choices for Honda Clutch motorbikes: 1. Honda Sonic 2. Honda CBR 3. Honda CRF
The following are the options for Yamaha Matic motorbikes: 1. Yamaha FreeGo 2. Yamaha Mio 3. Yamaha Fino
The following are the choices for the Yamaha Moped motorbike: 1. Yamaha MX King 2. Yamaha Jupiter 3. Yamaha Vega Force
The following are the options for Yamaha Clutch motorbikes: 1. Yamaha XSR 2. Yamaha R15 3. Yamaha Vixion
